ymmsl_version: v0.2

description: |
  # Example yMMSL file containing run configuration

  To run the coupled model, additional information can be specified, like how many
  resources to use for each submodel and when to write a snapshot, if the programs used
  support it.

resources:
  macro:
    threads: 1
  micro:
    mpi_processes: 8

checkpoints:
  at_end: true
  simulation_time:
  - every: 50
